<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><code>[[cal.chronicle D M Y to D M Y]]</code> enricher with locked-range Chronicle</li>
      <li>Bastion facility orders auto-advance with world time (dnd5e)</li>
      <li>Calendar exports bundle referenced weather presets</li>
      <li>Chat <code>/advance</code> triggers cinematic; <code>cinematic=</code> override supported</li>
      <li>Duplicate button on climate zones</li>
      <li>PF2E/SF2E WorldClock sync works with every bundled calendar</li>
      <li>Per-phase Weight values on Randomized moons</li>
      <li>Per-zone fixed sunrise/sunset hours</li>
      <li>Rest advance dropdown: 8 AM, Sunrise, or Fixed Hours</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Canonical corrections to 14 prebuilt calendars</li>
      <li>Climate zone temperature inheritance saving as 0/19 or 0/20</li>
      <li>Forecast variance escaping season/zone valid presets</li>
      <li>Multi-million-iteration freeze on recurring notes with stale start dates</li>
      <li>Per-user note permissions lost when toggling visibility</li>
      <li>Settings panel crash on legacy custom theme data</li>
      <li>Slash commands silently failing in Foundry v13+ chat</li>
      <li>Weather Picker leaving temperature blank after preset selection</li>
      <li>Week view not rendering recurring notes on every matching day</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Changes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Bundled calendar count reduced to 19 (<code>khorvaire</code>/<code>greyhawk-364</code> consolidated)</li>
      <li>Duration controls moved to the Schedule tab; limited-repeat removed</li>
      <li>Golarion, Golarion Imperial, and Pact Standard now use Gregorian leap rules</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
